00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,480
You look tired,Simon.
你看起来很累, Simon.

2
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:17,130
Didn't you sleep well last night?
你昨晚没睡好吗?

3
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:19,620
I had a very strange dream.
我做了个奇怪的梦.

4
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:20,600
Yeah?
是吗?

5
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:23,120
I went to Scotland to play golf.
我去苏格兰打高尔夫球.

6
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,470
That's not so strange.
那不奇怪呢.

7
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:27,820
But I played an amazing game.
但是我玩了一场神奇的比赛.

8
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:30,050
After the first seventeen holes,
在最初的17个洞之后,

9
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:31,770
my score was seventeen.
我的得分是17杆.

10
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:32,700
Seventeen?
17杆?

11
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:33,680
Seventeen.
17杆.

12
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:36,650
That means you hit seventeen holes-in-one.
那意味着你打了17个一杆进洞(holes-in-one)

13
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:37,780
One after another.
一个接着一个.

14
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:49,140
I hit that ball.
我击中球.

15
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,440
It flew through the air,landed,
它飞过空气, 落地,

16
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,380
and rolled into the waiting cup.
然后滚进下一个洞.

17
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:55,180
That's a great dream.
那真是一个很棒的梦.

18
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:56,530
I could do no wrong.
我怎么打都不会出错.

19
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,700
Until the eighteenth hole.
直到第18个洞.

20
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:00,130
What happened?
发生了什么?

21
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,700
It started fine.
开始挺好.

22
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:03,800
I drove onto the green.
我(把球)打到了球穴区(the green).

23
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,950
I was about three feet away from golfing history..
我距离创造历史只有3英尺(feet)

24
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:09,920
the lowest score ever.
史上最低分数(杆数).

25
00:01:12,709 --> 00:01:15,136
Simon.What happened next?
Simon. 然后发生了什么?

26
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:17,620
Ninety-four putts.
94杆(putts).

27
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,040
That's no dream. That a nightmare.
那不是梦. 那是噩梦.

